text:
@ParadisLabs Analyst reports were at €18 and €21 fair price, and they both owned the stonk 😂

"AI Photonics" segment is small in the structure of the company, and those mobile metrology machines they have as product.... don't know, look a bit 🥴

Where do you see the great thing here?

AI is moving beyond chips—into photonics and space-based connectivity as data demand outgrows copper networks.

@SC_FUNDS highlights Lumentum $LITE, Corning $GLW, and Coherent $COHR driving this shift. Watch Markets in Motion.

#AI #Investing #Photonics #SpaceEconomy #StockMarket https://t.co/3QAiQGqnrs

